data.description: NEWLY PRICED....ELEGANCE with STYLE - Portobello Road - Impressive custom designed 4BR/3.5BA brick home. Two-story foyer w/marble floors, dining, living w/FP, library, gourmet kitchen w/granite, island, eating bar, glass display area, breakfast area has glass display, great room w/coffered ceiling and FP, master bedroom has sitting area, huge master bath w/walk-in closet, 2nd floor features 3BR/2BA, office/den, family room, exercise room, rec. room. Basement has den w/FP & 1 car garage/ w/FP.
